               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17431207-38-off207-c238" targOrder="Y" targets="t17431207-38-defend316 t17431207-38-off207 t17431207-38-verdict209"></join>
         
               <p>45. 
               
                  <persName id="t17431207-38-defend316" type="defendantName">
                     Thomas 
                     Clarke 
                  <interp inst="t17431207-38-defend316" type="surname" value="Clarke"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-defend316" type="given" value="Thomas"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-defend316" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             , of <placeName id="t17431207-38-defloc206">St. Mary Abchurch</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17431207-38-defloc206" type="placeName" value="St. Mary Abchurch"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17431207-38-defloc206" type="type" value="defendantHome"></interp>
                  <join result="persNamePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17431207-38-defend316 t17431207-38-defloc206"></join>, was indicted for <rs id="t17431207-38-off207" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-off207" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-off207" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing six Yards of Linen Cloth, Value 4 s.
            </rs> the Goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17431207-38-victim318" type="victimName">
                     Richard 
                     Glover 
                  <interp inst="t17431207-38-victim318" type="surname" value="Glover"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-victim318" type="given" value="Richard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-victim318" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17431207-38-off207 t17431207-38-victim318"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17431207-38-cd208" type="crimeDate">Nov. 29</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17431207-38-off207 t17431207-38-cd208"></join>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17431207-38-person319">
                  Christian 
                  Wagner 
               <interp inst="t17431207-38-person319" type="surname" value="Wagner"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-person319" type="given" value="Christian"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-person319" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live with Mr. Glover, and he having lost several pieces of Cloth out of the Warehouse, I had a Suspicion of the Prisoner; the Prisoner was sent for, to do a Job in the Warehouse; I placed myself so that I could see what he did; he presently came down, and as soon as he thought himself alone, he took a piece of Linen out of a Chest, opened it, and put it between his Waistcoat and Shirt, so that he did not look as if he had any Bundle about him; I challenged him with it, stripped him, and took it from him before he went out of the House. <rs id="t17431207-38-verdict209" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-verdict209" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17431207-38-punish210" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-punish210" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17431207-38-punish210" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="branding"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17431207-38-defend316 t17431207-38-punish210"></join>
               
                     <note>[Branding. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
